    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sports coupe offers a refined driving experience for the discerning enthusiast. The exterior is finished in a striking metallic charcoal that retains a brilliant shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium leather upholstery is supple, showing only slight entry-wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio and a recently completed major interval service. It sits on a set of high-performance tires with plenty of tread remaining, ensuring a tight, responsive feel on every corner. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that has been treated with respect by its previous owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
