    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really wonderful shape! It runs smoothly, has been well-cared for, and is honestly just a blast to drive. Whether you need a dependable daily commuter or something fun for weekend road trips, this car is ready to go. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner very happy! Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
