    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving peak, featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The drivetrain remains robust, with the M-Variable Differential Lock providing predictable lock-up for optimal power delivery. Maintenance is current, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a reinforced rear subframe to address known chassis fatigue. Suspension geometry is preserved with refreshed bushings and upgraded Bilstein dampers for superior rebound characteristics. While the exterior displays minor road-going patina, the engine\u2019s internal harmonics and compression are excellent, offering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
